        "timestamp": "2018-02-08 17:55:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nTrying to understand why the init container chmod script section in the es deployment yaml is required  It looks like you have found a fix for\nhttps://jira.onap.org/browse/OOM-510\n\n\n  - command:\n        - /bin/sh\n        - -c\n        - |\n          sysctl -w vm.max_map_count=262144\n          mkdir -p /logroot/elasticsearch/logs\n          mkdir -p /logroot/elasticsearch/data\n          chmod -R 777 /logroot/elasticsearch\n          chown -R root:root /logroot",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
